Who We Are
Kooply ZYP,
sometimes doing business as K-Creative
, offers
          mobile games through our mobile apps and manages Branching Factor’s
          games. Our offices are located at
12 Hatzofim Rishon Lezion IL
and our registration number is
516471851
.
If you have questions about our company or your privacy, or want to
          exercise your rights, or you just want to say hello, you can contact
          us at
hello@kooply.com
.
If you have specific requests under European law, you can also
          contact us, by way of our representative in the European Union (EU),
          PrighterGDPR-Rep
by Maetzler Rechtsanwalts GmbH &Co KG, using the information
