          identifiers in order to serve you with targeted ads on our apps. By
          collecting this information, we get insights into your preferences and
          interests and we are better able to serve you with ads that we believe
          will appeal to you.
Marketing Campaigns.
In addition, we do run marketing campaigns on other platforms
          in order to let people know about our Services. As part of these
          campaigns, we may receive a hashed ID relating to your device. This
          can help us track the success of our campaigns.
