          be subject to the provisions of this Privacy Notice
.
Law Enforcement Related Disclosure
. We may share your personal data with government agencies or other
          relevant parties, such as a law office or independent auditor: (i) if
          we believe that such disclosure is appropriate to protect our rights,
          property or safety (including the enforcement of the Terms and this
          Privacy Notice) or those of a third party; (ii) if required by law or
          court order; or (iii) as is necessary to comply with any legal and/or
          regulatory obligations, such as audit requirements.
